c: 12
v: 23
t: "And who (F) he is in her house/home seduced/enticed him from himself, and she closed/shut the doors/entrances, and said: \"Come/come here .\" He said: \"I seek protection (of) God, that He is my Lord, He did good/beautified my residence/home , that He does not make the unjust/oppressive succeed/win"